{"tid":1514863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(求原圖) Together we fight and sun will rise","createTime":"2019-08-29T02:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T02:58:58.000Z","uid":124894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0570be23541c545dd483444ae18aba7c3b6c525","tid":1514863,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qegsv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qegsv2.jpg&h=3a62033c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnmKBph.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnmKBph.png&h=1c2f8566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efuHn4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefuHn4j.jpg&h=de6c473f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無呢輯所有相嘅2K原圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f1e9bee03718eb79880ead6791807a6c9fa541","tid":1514863,"uid":183536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:28:57.000Z","msg":"有時有戰友好簡單話，&ldquo;美國為利益唔會救我地架&rdquo;。有時又有戰友鍾意講: &ldquo;侵侵萬歲!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n其實又係時候提提大家，美國在港利益有幾個痛點，不一定和其他西方國家一致:<br />\n<br />\n1. 不容翻版商品流通/出入口，導致美商版稅損失<br />\n2. 不容軍事科技經香港流入中國，影響美國國家安全<br />\n3. 希望美軍艦艇能依照1997年前一樣，定期入港 (雖然可以去泰國、菲律賓或台灣)<br />\n4. 每年對香港有巨大貿易順差，還有無數美資公司在港，希望繼續賺錢<br />\n5. 香港有大約8萬美國籍公民需要照顧<br />\n6. 香港和台灣，從來都是整個中美關係的兩隻棋子<br />\n<br />\n要照顧美國在港利益，需不需要支持香港的民主普選，要看說。客。的。功。力。對美方來說，沒有絕對的答案。因為大部分美國人，其實對香港的事務不太熟悉。而在六月的示威前，香港人權及民主法案拖延多時，大家現在大概明白什麼事吧。<br />\n<br />\n若無民主，就無法治!若無法治， 定必逃稅!關稅齊一，我要攬炒!<br />\n<br />\nAdditional tariff to China, first additional tariff to Hong Kong!<br />\n#MakeAmericaGreatAgain <br />\n#FightforFairTrade<br />\n#TariffHKnChinaTogether <br />\n#PassHKHumanRightsDemocracyAct #AbolishHKSeparateCustomsTerritory<br />\n#liberateHK <br />\n#StandwithHK <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVs9NxA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVs9NxA.png&h=1584ccb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f7a4538890be4e092b0bb5d0f2e4140b355f459","tid":1514863,"uid":56305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n擺twitter都好呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DcKgsi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcKgsi1.jpg&h=2255b060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9OkTY2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9OkTY2.jpg&h=f2327ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBH9Ni2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBH9Ni2.jpg&h=48d188b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzhNyY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzhNyY3.jpg&h=ae1b4798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTryuxp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTryuxp.jpg&h=1dffdbd1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}